</p><p>
<b>Information that we automatically receive</b>
</p><p>
Etelegate receives and stores certain information whenever you download web pages, or send us e-mail or forms.  For example:
</p><p>
1. We identify the numerical IP address assigned to your computer by your Internet Service Provider.
</p><p>
