</p><p>
<b>Protection of your privacy</b>
</p><p>
Etelegate will release data when we believe the release is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our Agreement, and protect the contract rights of our Clients.  Etelegate passes the following data to the owner/operator of the website from which you are purchasing services utilizing Etelegate’s services:
